1
00:01:56,490 --> 00:02:01,230
The Untamed

2
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:04,850
Episode 03

3
00:02:06,090 --> 00:02:07,320
=Jinzhenhe Tavern

4
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,440
Waiter, what happened?

5
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,880
How can you suddenly run out of room?

6
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:10,470
Sir.

7
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,040
This is not our intention at all.

8
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:12,920
Today

9
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,880
here suddenly came an influential Childe.

10
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,600
He booked the whole tavern

11
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:19,320
and drove everyone out, except his people.

12
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,240
Sir, I'm sorry but I assume

13
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,920
it's better to find another tavern.

14
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:23,640
Waiter!

15
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,200
Oh, Misses.

16
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,720
According to your order

17
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:27,760
all rooms have been tidied.

18
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:30,600
And we have also sent other guests away.

19
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,560
Please take these perfume bags.

20
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:34,040
And put them in our Childe Jin's room.

21
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,680
With chopped herbs inside

22
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,160
they can keep mosquitoes at bay.

23
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,120
Mianmian, how considerate you are!

24
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,800
No wonder our Childe favors you.

25
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,640
Stop that.

26
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,240
You shall be careful of this matter

27
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,480
taking the renown of our Childe into account.

28
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:49,480
Please rest assured. I fully understand.

29
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:50,560
Let's go

30
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,160
to see our Childe's room.

31
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,040
Please go this way, Misses.

32
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,920
I see. They are the Jin clan of Lanling.

33
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,760
They must be here for the lecture too

34
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,640
and taking a rest in Caiyi town.

35
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,360
Brother,

36
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,240
such a few people of Jin clan

37
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,800
occupy the whole tavern

38
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,560
and want to drive us away despite the sequence.

39
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,760
But there is no vacant tavern left in the town.

40
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,240
We have no choice.

41
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,000
Lady Mianmian!

42
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:46,640
May I have one of your perfume bags?

43
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,200
Who are you?

44
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,840
Who gave you the right to call me Mianmian?

45
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:53,600
It's her.

46
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,960
She may call you Mianmian.

47
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,280
Why can't I?

48
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,120
Who on earth are you?

49
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:00,360
Don't call me like that!

50
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,160
All right.

51
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,360
What about you telling me your true name?

52
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,720
Then I won't call you Mianmain.

53
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:09,880
Why should I tell you as you ask?

54
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,480
You should say your own name

55
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,480
before asking somebody else's name.

56
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,760
That's easy.

57
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:17,040
I'll say, keep it in mind.

58
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:20,200
My name is Yuandao.

59
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,720
Yuandao...

60
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:23,880
Mianmian

61
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:28,360
I can't remember which clan's childe bears this name.

62
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,280
But judging from his look and demeanor

63
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,640
he's not like a nobody.

64
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:35,880
You...

65
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,840
You teased  me!

66
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,240
What happened?

67
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,440
Think about the poetry.

68
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,720
What's next to "green, green,the riverside grass"

69
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,920
Green, green, the riverside grass

70
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,800
Long, long, missing that far road.
(also can be seen as "Mianmian misses Yuandao" )

71
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,760
Don't speak that out!

72
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,880
Who misses you?

73
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,400
How shameless.

74
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:59,360
Say, Lady Mainmian, you come from Jin clan of Lanling, right?

75
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:04,320
People say girls from Jin clan are all pretty as fairies.

76
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,160
Now that I have seen one

77
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:07,320
I can't agree more.

78
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,960
Glib-tongued.

79
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:15,200
I am Wei Ying from Jiang clan of Yunmeng.

80
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,200
My courtesy name is Wuxian.

81
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,000
We're going to the Lan clan of Gusu for the lecture

82
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,920
and taking a rest in Caiyi town.

83
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,640
As fellow cultivators,

84
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:24,960
Lady Mianmian won't bear to see us sleep out on the streets.

85
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:29,280
So, Mr. Yuandao

86
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,640
you do have a decent name.

87
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,160
However...

88
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:35,600
as for the rooms...

89
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:36,600
Mianmian,

90
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:40,200
our Childe won't bring so many people here anyway.

91
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,240
These rooms are vacant for nothing.

92
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,280
Not to mention they arrived earlier.

93
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,200
Such being the case,

94
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,600
Childe Wei, you and your party may stay.

95
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,560
And I won't bother our Childe with this matter.

96
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:54,640
Ladies, much obliged.

97
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,560
Only a frivolous playboy like you

98
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,600
can take the rooms back from those girls.

99
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,640
Senior Sister,

100
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,080
listen to what he said!

101
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:07,600
Jiang Cheng,

102
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,680
I'll generouly take that

103
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:11,960
as your envy and jealousy of me.

104
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,760
How about you two fighting it out here and now?

105
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,920
But, senior sister,

106
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:21,840
who is the Childe Jin Mianmian mentioned?

107
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,080
Who else could it be?

108
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,600
Approximate age as us

109
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,760
and a Jin clan.

110
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,080
If it's not the youngest Childe, Jin Zixuan

111
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,040
who else could it be?

112
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,160
I just wonder if such Childe Jin

113
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,840
is still fancy like he was

114
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,490
when he was a child.

115
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,400
Lady and gentlemen,

116
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,200
I'm terribly sorry but

117
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,720
there aren't enough rooms.

118
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:48,720
Please empty these rooms as well.

119
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,360
Childe Jin.

120
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,520
This is the best tavern in the Caiyi town?

121
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,680
Yes, Childe.

122
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,920
Still no comparison to Jinlintai even as the best.

123
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,080
As for the chair,

124
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,080
we Jin clan make them out of black sandalwood.

125
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,000
As for the teacup,

126
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:16,400
we adopt only peacock green glaze porcelain.

127
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:22,930
The tea is stale.

128
00:07:22,930 --> 00:07:23,640
= Jin Zixuan from Jin clan of Lanling =
The tea is stale.

129
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,530
= Jin Zixuan from Jin clan of Lanling =

130
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,800
Let's go check the rooms.

131
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,480
This way, Childe.

132
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,680
Jiang clan of Yunmeng, pleased to see you.

133
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:12,960
I suppose junior Childe Jin

134
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,760
is also going to Lan clan of Gusu as an auditor, right?

135
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,600
Watch your manner!

136
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,760
Our childe is Childe Jin

137
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,880
not junior Childe Jin.

138
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:24,400
Childe Jiang is also passing by this place?

139
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,120
Yes, we need to take a rest here.

140
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,920
Unfortunately

141
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,800
every room in this tavern has been booked

142
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,600
by us Jin clan of Lanling

143
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:35,030
You guys better go elsewhere.

144
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:36,030
Hey,

145
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:37,840
but we arrived earlier.

146
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,030
You are earlier, so what?

147
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,080
You should go complain to the owner.

148
00:08:41,790 --> 00:08:43,240
Anyway, we have booked the whole tavern.

149
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:45,160
Our Childe would rather not

150
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:47,280
have association with some random folks.

151
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,960
As for the lecture of Lan clan

152
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,680
only a few quotas available for each clan.

153
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:01,560
Junior Childe Jin, you brought out a grand display

154
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:02,960
with so many people.

155
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,200
What's your purpose?

156
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:06,600
We're Childe Jin's servants. What's wrong?

157
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:12,000
So it's real that the Jin clan is ostentatious.

158
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,160
But I heard

159
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:19,960
the Lan clan is strict and puritanical.

160
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:23,000
Junior Childe Jin

161
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,120
takes so many retinues.

162
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,320
I'm really afraid

163
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,880
that you couldn't stand that kind of suffering.

164
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,160
Xian.

165
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:36,400
Senior Sister.

166
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,160
I'm just providing

167
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,920
a friendly suggestion.

168
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,920
How dare you insult our Childe!

169
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,760
Where is the manner of Jiang clan?

170
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,720
What insult?

171
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:45,800
Name it.

172
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:46,880
And

173
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,920
you can confront me

174
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:51,320
but don't involve Jiang clan of Yunmeng.

175
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,560
Xian, Cheng.

176
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,560
Go pack up.

177
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,200
We'll find another place.

178
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,880
Goodbye, Childe Jin.

179
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,560
Childe.

180
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,120
Your room is the next one.

181
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,640
Forgive me, Miss Jiang.

182
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:00,160
I'm mistaken about the room

183
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:01,440
No offence.

184
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,440
You are too modest to say that.

185
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,480
Isn't the whole tavern yours?

186
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:18,680
It's said that the etiquette of Jin clan is of high reputation.

187
00:11:19,225 --> 00:11:21,225
Now I can say just so so.

188
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:57,840
This Jin Zixuan,

189
00:11:58,040 --> 00:12:00,040
how arrogant he is!

190
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,240
Yeah.

191
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:03,480
He is flaunting just like a peacock.

192
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,400
It's a pity that

193
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,840
I couldn't even touch the pot of  Emperor's Smile.

194
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:10,240
Look at our situation.

195
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,440
You're still thinking about liquor?

196
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:14,040
Can't you see the look on senior sister'face?

197
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:27,400
I just don't know what Uncle Jiang was thinking.

198
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,480
Why did he arrange marriage

199
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,080
between senior sister and that peacock?

200
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,160
According to Lan clan's principles

201
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,520
everyone coming for the lecture

202
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,520
is not allowed in without an invitation.

203
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,440
Oh, buddy,

204
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:54,200
I've told you a thousand times.

205
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:56,520
We accidentally got our invitations lost.

206
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,120
We never intended to lose it.

207
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,080
What's more.

208
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:01,200
All of us are standing here.

209
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,440
What can we lie to you?

210
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,400
Sir,

211
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:04,360
without an invitation,

212
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,040
I can't identify you people.

213
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:10,480
Look, sun is about to set.

214
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,320
You can't just watch us sleeping out on the streets,

215
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,000
can you?

216
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,400
How about this.

217
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:16,560
Please go fetch your clan leader.

218
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,240
He had seen our senior sister.

219
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:19,600
At sight of her

220
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:21,480
he will know we're talking honestly.

221
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:23,840
Well then, please wait here for a moment

222
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:26,120
until we change shifts when it's 17:45.

223
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,000
17:45?

224
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,560
The sun has already set then.

225
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:30,440
Xian.

226
00:13:30,880 --> 00:13:31,680
Behave yourself.

227
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:34,480
But senior sister...

228
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,560
As father instructed

229
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,840
no matter when

230
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,320
we can't forget our manners.

231
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:45,480
Let's leave the gate and plan for the next step.

232
00:14:02,190 --> 00:14:03,630
= Lan Zhan, courtesy name is Wangji =

233
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,720
Second Childe, welcome back.

234
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,720
Who are looking for trouble?

235
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:16,720
This Second Childe of Lan

236
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,480
must be Lan Wangji, one of the twin jades of Lan,

237
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,600
and the younger brother of their clan leader Lan Xichen.

238
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,880
He must be our key to get in.

239
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,600
What happened?

240
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:38,440
Just carry him inside.

241
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,400
How can he end up like this?

242
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:43,280
End?

243
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,360
He's not dead if I say.

244
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,800
He's more like cursed by some wicked sorcery.

245
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,360
Wicked sorcery?

246
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:54,680
Second Childe Lan

247
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,040
I am Jiang Cheng from Jiang clan of Yunmeng,

248
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,680
son of our clan leader Jiang Fengmian.

249
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,240
This is my sister,  Jiang Yanli.

250
00:15:00,075 --> 00:15:01,355
My senior brother, Wei Ying, also called Wei Wuxian.

251
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,280
Second Childe Lan, we've heard much about you.

252
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:09,720
My honor.

253
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:11,760
Second Childe Lan,

254
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:13,160
we accidentally got our invitation lost.

255
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,200
It's getting late and inconvenient to sleep outside.

256
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,040
Please make a merciful exception for us.

257
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:19,680
No invitation, no entry.

258
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,200
Second Childe Lan,

259
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,760
we come all the way from Yunmeng.

260
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,480
Despite the exhausting travel

261
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,680
we finally made it before sunset

262
00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:28,040
to the Cloud Recesses.

263
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:30,600
You just turn us down for an invitation.

264
00:15:30,650 --> 00:15:32,370
Don't you think it's a little rigid?

265
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:36,080
No invitation, no entry.

266
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,800
Second Childe Lan,

267
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,360
it was an accident.

268
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,680
We never intended to lose it.

269
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:41,880
Please make an exception.

270
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:43,960
Find it and come back.

271
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:46,080
Second Childe Lan,

272
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:47,960
sun is about to set,

273
00:15:48,400 --> 00:15:51,040
while we are more than 20 miles away from Caiyi town.

274
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,600
You ask us to find it now.

275
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,240
What an imposition!

276
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:56,880
Second Childe Lan,

277
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:58,480
in the worst case we can...

278
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:09,280
Second Childe has put silencing charm on you.

279
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:10,840
