00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:36,880
to test this shard of Yin Iron?

565
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:40,920
Xue Yang,

566
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:44,360
you dare talk to me like that.

567
00:37:45,160 --> 00:37:47,160
What a daredevil.

568
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:00,840
I don't fear death.

569
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:03,160
I fear boredom.

570
00:38:03,720 --> 00:38:07,280
You help me find other three shards of Yin Iron

571
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:09,800
and subdue all other clans.

572
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:12,960
Then you can call your life worthwhile.

573
00:38:25,150 --> 00:38:26,590
Please don't forget, Your Excellency.

574
00:38:27,120 --> 00:38:29,760
I don't have the slightest interest in dominating others.

575
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:34,120
My request has been given

576
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:36,280
the first time I came to the Nevernight to see you.

577
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,720
I hope Your Excellency don't forget it.

578
00:38:39,240 --> 00:38:40,360
Don't worry.

579
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:43,600
Once I've collected all four shards of Yin Iron

580
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:47,280
your wish will definitely be fulfilled.

581
00:38:48,040 --> 00:38:49,800
Thank you in advance, Your Excellency.

582
00:38:54,440 --> 00:38:55,320
Xue Yang.

583
00:38:57,760 --> 00:39:00,720
West of Dafan, East of Gusu, North of Yueyang.

584
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:04,120
where is the last shard of Yin Iron?

585
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:08,160
Don't forget the promise between us, Your Excellency.

586
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,280
When Your Excellency ask me

587
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:12,880
to go to Chang clan of Yueyang for that shard of Yin Iron

588
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:15,280
I will tell you the last part then.

